<item>
            <title>[LU-17634] Reading a HSM released file in parallel on a client may return &quot;No data available&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17634</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For a file in HSM released, exists, archived status, start tens of processes to read it in parallel. Possibly one cat process reports &quot;No data available&quot; error. The file data is always fetched successfully later.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
